{"tid":2272592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"『美國大選』若選舉人跑票會怎樣？","createTime":"2020-11-05T06:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T18:43:58.000Z","uid":281328,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d4088e737754e4251e85ddfb6849c13ea2e9465f","tid":2272592,"uid":281328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T06:59:57.000Z","msg":"有21州並未規定選舉人必須依照普選結果投票，另有29州規定，失信的選舉人會遭處罰，華盛頓州對失信選舉人罰款1000美元（約32000元台幣），在南卡羅萊納州，失信的選舉人可能面臨刑事起訴。美國史上共有100多人曾經跑票，但比例甚小，從未影響過大選結果。<br />\n<br />\n2016年時美國總統選舉，最終總共有7名失信候選人跑票，其中5名該投希拉蕊，另兩名該投川普，失信選舉人人數創下歷史之最。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201104/TVIKCDZQK5HIPGDGHE46HXJ25Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201104%2FTVIKCDZQK5HIPGDGHE46HXJ25Q%2F&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4O6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=95e20b04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201104%2FTVIKCDZQK5HIPGDGHE46HXJ25Q%2F&h=e420f313\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201104/TVIKCDZQK5HIPGDGHE46HXJ25Q/</a>"},{"pid":"dda1e15f54872ec08ffdb0440998ce94c05db8c0","tid":2272592,"uid":281328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T07:03:49.000Z","msg":"今屆拜登會走幾多票？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6d19c0afb96cf8958706d59690d32b87d8a4ec","tid":2272592,"uid":281328,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T07:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果拜登270票當選<br />\n真係走一張選舉人票救全國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ded13b435225d70ee5a927eb6decf1a6086c03","tid":2272592,"uid":323720,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ec6d19c0afb96cf8958706d59690d32b87d8a4ec","tid":2272592,"uid":281328,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T07:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"